"{    \"translations\": [        {            \"english_version\": \"Centcom says it hit 90 Iranian targets in the latest strikes. The Iranian health ministry says 14 people were killed since Tuesday.\",            \"english_title\": \"Centcom Strikes Iranian Targets\",            \"translated_version\": \"Centcom dice que golpe\u00f3 90 objetivos iran\u00edes en los \u00faltimos ataques. El ministerio de salud de Ir\u00e1n dice que 14 personas murieron desde el martes.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Centcom ataca objetivos iran\u00edes\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"The attacks seem to be part of Ukraine's effort to cut off supplies and routes into and out of occupied Crimea. Data shows fewer ships, many carrying oil and gas, going through the waterway after attacks this week.\",            \"english_title\": \"Ukraine's Effort to Cut Off Crimea\",            \"translated_version\": \"Los ataques parecen ser parte del esfuerzo de Ucrania para cortar suministros y rutas hacia y desde Crimea ocupada. Los datos muestran menos barcos, muchos con petr\u00f3leo y gas, pasando por el agua despu\u00e9s de los ataques esta semana.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Esfuerzo de Ucrania para cortar Crimea\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"Two men with links to Ukraine's security services are accused of killing Anastasiia Berezovska and dumping her body in woods. Her body was found in a pond on Sunday, a day after her family reported her missing.\",            \"english_title\": \"Men Accused of Killing Anastasiia\",            \"translated_version\": \"Dos hombres con v\u00ednculos a los servicios de seguridad de Ucrania son acusados de matar a Anastasiia Berezovska y dejar su cuerpo en el bosque. Su cuerpo fue encontrado en un estanque el domingo, un d\u00eda despu\u00e9s de que su familia la report\u00f3 como desaparecida.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Hombres acusados de matar a Anastasiia\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"Aid worker Mohammed al-Wahidi became a well-known humanitarian figure during the Israel-Hamas war.\",            \"english_title\": \"Mohammed al-Wahidi: Humanitarian Figure\",            \"translated_version\": \"El trabajador de ayuda Mohammed al-Wahidi se hizo una figura humanitaria conocida durante la guerra Israel-Hamas.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Mohammed al-Wahidi: Figura humanitaria\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"The shares are set to start trading on the Nasdaq on Friday. This will be the largest ever debut by a foreign firm.\",            \"english_title\": \"Largest Foreign Firm Debut on Nasdaq\",            \"translated_version\": \"Las acciones comenzar\u00e1n a cotizar en el Nasdaq el viernes. Este ser\u00e1 el debut m\u00e1s grande de una empresa extranjera.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Mayor debut de empresa extranjera en Nasdaq\"        }    ]}"